      "html": "<p>\"报纸漫画条,\" 1852年，复数名词形式，源自 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of funny \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/funny\">funny</a>（形容词）。</p>"
